{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"ug5b9frm3w0fz4400egy5wi","title":"React Patterns","desc":"","updated":1734005270177,"created":1733912458137,"custom":{},"fname":"learning.react.react-patterns","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Harshita-notes","sync":"sync"},"contentHash":"57deb343f4db60b44f74f8409bde9081","links":[],"anchors":{"layout-components":{"type":"header","text":"Layout components","value":"layout-components","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"key-concepts":{"type":"header","text":"key concepts","value":"key-concepts","line":15,"column":0,"depth":3},"example":{"type":"header","text":"example","value":"example","line":20,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":["dv1l5xhkn1iaeker7ik3ea3","ahur9u8a8yj3xkacx0cqjt2","rasdv9a9uhtdt100mwt80cx","xqgcm6m5nb6dc5ybk4aqgyc","cnsrds3146uzfbzkaer0tav","umv1qlgcft10gzj348d0ou0","sojbzhwx1losfnysmamz42a"],"parent":"8fp89ktw3fhi2p6bt35b5ju","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"react-patterns\">React Patterns<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#react-patterns\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"layout-components\">Layout components<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#layout-components\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>design pattern used to structure the layout of a React application</li>\n<li>focus on organizing other components within a web page. like split screen, lists, modal</li>\n<li>promotes code reusability, separation of concerns, and a clean, organized codebase.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"key-concepts\">key concepts<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#key-concepts\"></a></h3>\n<p>the core components of our page should be unaffected by its placement.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>reusability</li>\n<li>separation of concerns: separating layout logic from business logic, you can focus on the specific responsibilities of each component. </li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"example\">example<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#example\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>for split screen type of layouts we should try to keep the stylings in the parent components and not the individual left and right.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>for lists: example of reusability </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">\n<span class=\"token comment\">//RegularList.jsx</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\"><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">RegularList</span></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> items<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sourceName<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">ItemComponent</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>items<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">item<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> i</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">ItemComponent</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">key</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token spread\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token spread operator\">...</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>sourceName<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> item <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//SmallAuthorListItem.jsx</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\"><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">SmallAuthorListItem</span></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>author<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> age<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> author<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\"> Name: </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain-text\">, Age: </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>age<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// App.jsx</span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">RegularList</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">items</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>authors<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">sourceName</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">\"author\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">ItemComponent</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">SmallAuthorListItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">RegularList</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">items</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>books<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">sourceName</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">\"book\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">ItemComponent</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">SmallAuthorListItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/Frontend-JsDev-Handbook/notes/dv1l5xhkn1iaeker7ik3ea3\">Compound</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Frontend-JsDev-Handbook/notes/ahur9u8a8yj3xkacx0cqjt2\">Controlled Uncontrolled</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Frontend-JsDev-Handbook/notes/rasdv9a9uhtdt100mwt80cx\">Custom Hooks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Frontend-JsDev-Handbook/notes/xqgcm6m5nb6dc5ybk4aqgyc\">Functional Programming</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Frontend-JsDev-Handbook/notes/cnsrds3146uzfbzkaer0tav\">Higher Order Components</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Frontend-JsDev-Handbook/notes/umv1qlgcft10gzj348d0ou0\">Observer Pattern with events</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Frontend-JsDev-Handbook/notes/sojbzhwx1losfnysmamz42a\">Render Prop</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"dlb5bmx7v8f6otsgongz4vx","title":"Hi","desc":"","updated":1663067414354,"creat